race.comment: A small field but it's tough. KNEZE (2) has been around the mark his last two in stronger company. They have been off gates 11 and 10 and he jumps from the paint today. Flies this course and trip and gets his chance. GREY NORTHERN (6) didn't finish it off over longer at Dalby but was improved beaten 0.5L at the Sunshine Coast prior. That form would see him right in the finish. BAVARIAN LADY (4) flopped in the same contest at Dalby but was beaten 1L on a CL5 prior at the mile. Will go close with average luck from an awkward gate. BOWRIDER (1) has been racing in better class and his Gold Coast placing two back stacks up.
